                <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc.02381.002_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
                <p>
                    Copy verbatim of <gap reason="damage"/> J. H. Johnson to Walt Whitman.
                </p>
                <p>
                    January 5, 1875 <gap reason="damage"/> apologetic letter explaining itself <gap reason="damage"/>
                    well enough. <gap reason="damage"/>. When stuffing myself with <gap reason="damage"/>
                    stuff that is <gap reason="damage"/>often feel a tormenting desire to,
                    if the Author <gap reason="damage"/> <hi rend="underline">enjoy</hi> the pleasing consciousness of <gap reason="damage"/>
                    great work.<gap reason="damage"/>eight weeks I again address you
                    When about <unclear reason="illegible" resp="#ak" cert="low">Oct</unclear><gap reason="damage"/> (perhaps presumptuous, perhaps
                    scraps of your<gap reason="damage"/>three weeks later sent a paper <gap reason="damage"/>
                    The School Ope<gap reason="damage"/>some other articles which I <gap reason="damage"/>
                    I recognise are<gap reason="damage"/>pen. The feeling of exaltation is
                    enough to <gap reason="damage"/>[ac]cordingly I sent (Nov 6) a letter
                    I fear was taken<gap reason="damage"/><hi rend="underline">egotists</hi> <gap reason="damage"/>and a few days later<gap reason="damage"/>
                    <hi rend="underline">copied article<gap reason="damage"/></hi> of Sou[th] Carolina which I thought
                    might interest<gap reason="damage"/> man's <gap reason="illegible" quantity="7" unit="chars"/>. I wanted to
                    plan my past<gap reason="damage"/>. But, dear man, dont take <gap reason="damage"/>
                    for <hi rend="underline">a dissatis<gap reason="damage"/></hi> have and do think Calhoun and<gap reason="damage"/>
                    better expound<gap reason="damage"/>history and nature of the Union and Constitution
                    than Webster<gap reason="damage"/> Whitman. Only leave us <hi rend="underline">the benefit
                    of a doubt</hi> as to the Law point, or <gap reason="illegible" quantity="8" unit="chars"/> to hang our
                    self-respect and to ask the respect of our children. But it was
                    not my intention to <hi rend="underline">reproach you</hi> for taking the other side.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Further, if in any of my writing there has appeared a design to <hi rend="underline">celebrate
                        myself,</hi> it was<gap reason="damage"/>, I thought the more you could<gap reason="damage"/>
                    me, so much<gap reason="damage"/>would be <hi rend="underline">pleased with yourself<gap reason="damage"/></hi>
                    of my wa<gap reason="damage"/><hi rend="underline">glad to have done me so much good</hi>
                    (Perhaps you have<gap reason="damage"/>some harm. The money invested <unclear reason="damage" resp="#ak" cert="medium">at the</unclear>
                    <hi rend="underline">same time</hi>, an<gap reason="damage"/>of the Sieorias seems to be <hi rend="underline">money in</hi>
                    My life-long<gap reason="damage"/>lies idle. Tom Moore, Bu<gap reason="damage"/>
                    Bailey's "Fester<gap reason="damage"/>[bor]rowed and quickly returned<gap reason="damage"/>
                    aside. (<hi rend="underline">It was<gap reason="damage"/>hard life that made me fearful</hi><gap reason="damage"/>
                    Mo hear verna<gap reason="damage"/>it is "Leaves of Grass" at all<gap reason="damage"/>
                    hours. Am I<gap reason="damage"/><gap reason="illegible" quantity="9" unit="chars"/> ?[foolish], I have lent<gap reason="damage"/>
                    book a good<gap reason="damage"/>pleasure might not destroy all<gap reason="damage"/>
                </p>
                <p>
                    A good, good<gap reason="damage"/><hi rend="underline">every way.</hi> Our future<gap reason="damage"/>
                    <hi rend="underline">founded on</hi><gap reason="damage"/>man happy till he is dead<gap reason="damage"/>
                    <hi rend="underline">not then</hi>. (Only<gap reason="damage"/>&#8212;I&#8212;Please send at least one<gap reason="damage"/>
                    when convenient<gap reason="damage"/>subscribe to-day for the New Republic<gap reason="damage"/>
                    <hi rend="underline">the purpose</hi>, used<gap reason="damage"/>yet some news of you, dear man,
                    without troubling<gap reason="damage"/>any further. 
                </p>
                <closer><salute>J.N.Johnson</salute></closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>Copied from memory<gap reason="damage"/>post office.
                        <gap reason="illegible" quantity="3" unit="chars"/> note the<gap reason="damage"/>[rest]! <gap reason="illegible" quantity="4" unit="chars"/> 8</p>
                    <p>Meltonsville Ala
                    see other side</p>
