            <p>Please inform me as soon as possible of the <unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#js">contents</unclear> of Reg. Package Envelope No. 50 which was mailed from your office <choice><abbr>Jany</abbr><expan>January</expan></choice> 5th 1875.</p>
